title: Nutri Ninja® Blender System with Auto-iQ™ (BL680 Series)
description:
The  Nutri Ninja® Blender System with Auto-iQ (BL680 Series) offers a one touch solution to making delicious and nutritious smoothies, dips, purees and more

Our food processing blades enable you to chop vegetables quickly and evenly every time with no worry of over processing. 

Our Ninja ® Blender System with Auto-i provides professional performance with our XL 72 oz. blender pitcher, 8-cup food processor and our Nutri Ninja® cups.
